{
   "template":{
      "description":"This stress test will help an administrator find out what the pure framework oriented overhead of NiFi will be under load.  Specifically it generates as many flow files as possible as fast as possible, updates an attribute or two, and makes a simple routing decision.  All of this is aimed at putting pressure on the FlowFile repository and Provenance repositories.  It doesn't cause any IO nor anything really interesting in terms of CPU.",
      "name":"Stress Test: Framework",
